00:52:31.990 --> 00:52:34.600
to build better
technology for those

00:52:34.600 --> 00:52:36.790
that are often
overlooked in the West--

00:52:36.790 --> 00:52:39.670
poor people, beyond just
the cost of phone and sort

00:52:39.670 --> 00:52:42.130
of reducing access to
entry, actually building

00:52:42.130 --> 00:52:45.940
technology that serves at the
app level or one layer further,

00:52:45.940 --> 00:52:49.432
some of those more rural and
